name: Mysore Sandal Soap (HUL)
description: Made with pure sandalwood oil, Mysore Sandal Soap offers a luxurious bathing experience with a rich, natural fragrance. It nourishes the skin, leaving it soft and refreshed. Known for its heritage and Ayurvedic formulation, it’s a trusted choice for gentle, everyday cleansing.

name: Medimix 18 Herbs Soap
description: Infused with 18 Ayurvedic herbs, Medimix is designed to prevent skin issues like acne, body odor, and infections. It provides a natural, herbal cleanse while keeping the skin healthy and supple. Suitable for all skin types, it's especially popular for its medicinal benefits.

name: Cinthol Original Soap
description: Cinthol Original Soap, enriched with germ protection, offers a strong, refreshing aroma and deep cleansing. It helps protect against dust, pollution, and skin problems, making it ideal for active lifestyles. Its iconic legacy and freshness make it a go-to bath bar for many.

name: Patanjali Neem Kanti Soap
description: Made with neem, haldi, and other Ayurvedic ingredients, Patanjali Neem Kanti is an antibacterial soap aimed at treating pimples and skin irritation. It cleanses thoroughly while maintaining skin health, especially for oily or acne-prone skin. It’s a budget-friendly, herbal alternative.

name: Dove Beauty Bar
description: Dove Beauty Bar is more than just a soap—it’s a moisturizing cleanser with ¼ moisturizing cream. It gently nourishes dry skin without stripping natural oils. Known for its soft, creamy lather, Dove leaves skin smooth, soft, and radiant after every wash.

name: Lux Soft Touch Soap
description: Lux Soft Touch is infused with floral extracts and silk protein, offering a fragrant, creamy lather that leaves skin feeling soft and pampered. Designed for daily use, it enhances the bathing experience with its long-lasting fragrance and gentle moisturizing properties.

name: Dettol Original Soap
description: Dettol Original Soap provides trusted germ protection with every wash. Formulated with antibacterial agents, it helps prevent infection, body odor, and skin issues. Ideal for hygiene-conscious users, it’s a reliable choice for keeping skin clean and protected throughout the day.

name: Biotique Bio Almond Oil Soap
description: Biotique’s Bio Almond Oil Soap is an Ayurvedic, 100% natural bar enriched with almond oil, coconut oil, and wild turmeric. It deeply nourishes and softens skin, making it suitable for dry and sensitive skin types. It’s chemical-free and eco-friendly.

name: Pears Transparent Soap
description: Pears Soap is a gentle, glycerin-based cleanser known for its transparency and purity. It hydrates and refreshes skin while being dermatologically tested for sensitive skin. Its mild formula and light fragrance make it a popular choice for daily, gentle cleansing.

name: Himalaya Neem & Turmeric Soap
description: Himalaya Neem & Turmeric Soap combines neem’s antibacterial properties with turmeric’s healing benefits. It effectively combats acne and skin impurities while soothing and refreshing the skin. Ideal for oily or acne-prone skin, it offers a clean, herbal bath experience.

name: Parle-G
description: India’s favorite glucose biscuit, Parle-G is packed with energy and nostalgia. Ideal for tea-time or on-the-go snacking, it’s made with wheat flour and enriched with vitamins and iron. Loved by all age groups for its simple, sweet flavor and crunchy texture.

name: Britannia Good Day
description: Loaded with the richness of cashews and a buttery base, Good Day biscuits deliver a joyful crunch in every bite. With a melt-in-mouth texture and delicious aroma, these are perfect for elevating your tea-time or just a quick treat anytime.

name: Hide & Seek Fab
description: A delightful combination of crispy chocolate cookies and smooth chocolate cream, Hide & Seek Fab offers a fun and indulgent treat. Great for kids and chocolate lovers alike, it’s a perfect snack for school tiffins or evening cravings.

name: Marie Gold
description: Light, crisp, and low on sugar, Britannia Marie Gold is made from wheat and designed for the health-conscious. It pairs perfectly with tea and provides energy without being heavy. A wholesome and classic biscuit choice for daily snacking.

name: Treat Orange
description: Britannia Treat Orange sandwiches tangy orange-flavored cream between crispy biscuits. A hit among kids, it's playful, colorful, and full of fruity flavor. Great as a snack in lunchboxes or after-school munching.

name: Oreo
description: The world’s favorite cookie, Oreo features two rich cocoa biscuits with a delicious vanilla crème filling. Dunk it in milk, twist it apart, or eat it whole—Oreo is versatile and fun for all ages. Imported flavor in an Indian-friendly pack size.

name: Bourbon
description: Britannia Bourbon offers a timeless combination of crunchy chocolate biscuits filled with smooth chocolate cream, topped with sugar crystals. A chocolaty indulgence ideal for dessert moments, tea-time, or as a sweet treat on-the-go.

name: Milk Bikis
description: Fortified with milk and essential nutrients, Milk Bikis is a nutritious biscuit option for growing kids. With a crunchy texture and mild sweetness, it goes perfectly with milk and makes for a wholesome snack anytime of the day.

name: 50-50 Maska Chaska
description: Britannia 50-50 Maska Chaska offers a buttery, herby flavor with a perfect balance of sweet and salty. Ideal for light snacking, it delivers a savory burst of taste in every crunchy bite. A favorite among those who love bold yet smooth flavors.

name: Jim Jam
description: Britannia Jim Jam brings you cream-filled sandwich biscuits topped with a center of jam and sugar sprinkles. A delightful mix of vanilla, jammy fruitiness, and crunch—perfect for kids and those with a sweet tooth.

name: Nescafe Classic Instant
description: A timeless instant coffee made from pure Robusta beans, Nescafé Classic delivers a bold, full?flavored cup in seconds. Perfect for busy mornings or quick office breaks, it boasts a rich aroma and smooth finish, enriched with essential vitamins to give you an energizing start to your day.

name: Starbucks Pike Place Roast
description: Starbucks’ iconic medium?roast blend features balanced notes of cocoa and toasted nuts for a smooth, approachable cup. Pike Place Roast is slow?roasted to bring out its nuanced flavor and is perfect for drip, pour?over, or French press brewing—ideal for everyday coffee moments.

name: Bru Filter Coffee (Tata)
description: BRU Instant Coffee offers the authentic taste of South Indian coffee plantations in a convenient granule form. With a lively aroma and robust flavor, it dissolves instantly in hot water or milk. An energizing choice for those who love a quick, strong cup without compromising on quality.

name: Blue Tokai Medium Roast – 100?g
description: Specialty?grade Arabica beans, freshly roasted in India, give Blue Tokai Medium Roast a balanced profile of nuts and mild fruitiness. Its medium body and smooth finish suit drip, pour?over, or French press methods. Enjoy the freshness and nuanced flavors that make every sip exceptional.

name: Lavazza Qualità Rossa
description: An authentic Italian espresso blend of Arabica and Robusta beans, Qualità Rossa offers a full?bodied cup with chocolatey undertones and a warm, lingering finish. Perfect for moka pots or espresso machines, its rich crema and aroma transport you straight to your favorite café.

name: Death Wish Coffee
description: Billed as the world’s strongest coffee, Death Wish’s dark roast combines high?caffeine Robusta beans with premium Arabica for an intense kick and bold flavor. Its rich, smoky profile and smooth finish make it a cult favorite for those seeking an extra?powerful brew.

name: Tim Hortons Original
description: This classic Canadian medium?roast delivers a smooth, mellow cup with gentle sweetness and a clean finish. Tim Hortons Original is crafted for drip brewing, offering a comforting everyday coffee that’s both approachable and reliable—perfect for starting your morning off right.

name: Illy Classico Medium Roast
description: Illy’s signature Classico roast uses 100?% Arabica beans to achieve a harmonious balance of floral notes, caramel, and toasted bread. This medium?roast espresso grind produces a velvety crema and elegant aroma, ideal for moka pots and home espresso machines.

name: Café Du Monde Coffee & Chicory
description: A New Orleans tradition since 1862, this dark?roasted coffee is blended with chicory for a smooth, slightly woody flavor. Perfect for café au lait, its unique, comforting richness and the subtle earthiness of chicory make it an iconic, heartwarming brew.

name: Green Mountain Breakfast Blend
description: A bright, light?roast blend with balanced sweetness and a clean finish, this Breakfast Blend is specially portioned for Keurig® machines. Each pod brews a crisp, nutty cup—perfect for a morning pick?me?up with consistent quality and ease.
